      <title>斯里兰卡公司计划国家在未来几周内首次上市的Sukuk</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/sri-lanka-firm-aims-to-sell-nation-s-first-sukuk-in-coming-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡可再生能源生产国维达拉卡俱乐部（Vidullanka Plc）计划在当地博物会努力开展伊斯兰金融市场后的几周内，在接下来的几周内出售该国首个公开上市的Sukuk债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/sri-lanka-firm-aims-to-sell-nation-s-first-sukuk-in-coming-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 08:14:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
