      <title>毛里求斯试图稳定卢比，恢复证券交易所</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/mauritius-seeks-to-stabilize-rupee-revive-stock-exchange</link>
      <description><![CDATA[毛里求斯的新政府将优先考虑稳定货币的措施，并吸引外国投资者，以恢复其饱受折磨的证券交易所。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/mauritius-seeks-to-stabilize-rupee-revive-stock-exchange</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 08:10:38 GMT</pubDate>
