    <item>
      <title>德意志银行的DWS解决德国绿色调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/deutsche-bank-s-dws-settles-german-greenwashing-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行AG的投资部门DWS将支付数百万欧元，以结束德国检察官对所谓的绿色洗涤的长期调查，与2023年与美国监管机构达成的类似和解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/deutsche-bank-s-dws-settles-german-greenwashing-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 07:38:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着贸易商评估供应转变，天气，欧洲天然气会波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/european-gas-rises-amid-norwegian-maintenance-cooler-weather</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲天然气价格近42欧元，因为贸易商权衡了该地区燃料供应的变化以及从凉爽的起点到春季的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/european-gas-rises-amid-norwegian-maintenance-cooler-weather</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 07:05:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
