      <title>尼日利亚雇用壳牌部门的前首席执行官领导国家石油公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/nigeria-hires-ex-ceo-of-shell-unit-to-lead-state-oil-company</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂努布（Bola Tinubu）聘请了壳牌公司的前负责人来经营国家石油公司，因为非洲最大的原油生产商致力于提高产出和为首次公开募股做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/nigeria-hires-ex-ceo-of-shell-unit-to-lead-state-oil-company</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 05:33:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
